l%C3%A3o-ph%C3%B9ng-xu%C3%A2n/poem-exq2vy_L9f4mo6qpcj-Dag">Hoạ Thiệu Nghiêu Phu “Niên lão phùng xuân” - 和邵堯夫年老逢春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-Quang/author-7OFzGbIEkOgkM6aU4rZZZw">Tư Mã Quang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/Kinh-Ch%C3%A2u-h%E1%BA%ADu-kh%E1%BB%95-tuy%E1%BA%BFt-d%E1%BA%ABn/poem-u06Cqs7u1F0YDvHylKIiyA">Kinh Châu hậu khổ tuyết dẫn - 荊州後苦雪引</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/author-ZqGaWwKOrJXGaqhA3jlDaw">Viên Hoằng Đạo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-Kh%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%93/Quy-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Quan-th%E1%BB%A9-ni%C3%AAn-t%C3%A1c/poem-AHYPWJKhuNab78zyZhCh8Q">Quy Vương Quan thứ niên tác - 歸王官次年作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-Kh%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%93/author--S-Kylm25PBOdm26_KrpXQ">Tư Không Đồ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-V%E1%BB%8B-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/S%E1%BB%A9-L%C4%A9nh-Nam-v%C4%83n-Th%C3%B4i-M%C3%A3-nh%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-s%E1%BB%AD-b%C3%ADnh-b%C3%A1i-thai-lang/poem-zWjmnooiOf3KrQ-7Z2lnpA">Sứ Lĩnh Nam văn Thôi Mã nhị ngự sử bính bái thai lang - 使嶺南聞崔馬二御史并拜臺郎</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-V%E1%BB%8B-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/author-OeunXNYC4H8ZCUGbuTuz-A">Tô Vị Đạo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Th%C3%A1i-B%C3%ACnh-m%E1%BA%A1i-ca-gi%E1%BA%A3/poem-P3j-hu2ra9AUTYc_k_oguQ">Thái Bình mại ca giả - 太平賣歌者</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
